Class FlmCrew

java.lang.Object
  beans.FlmCrew

public class FlmCrew
extends java.lang.Object

Creates the ability to add a certain crewmember to a movie. This crewmember can have a specific role , but his information has to be in persons table. CrewMember will be saved into database.
